gates Incentives: TBD (Average Monthly ARB incentives: 108,7k)\n- Karma Administration Costs: 3750 ARB per month.\n- SEEDGov Administration Costs: 3.333 ARB per month.\n- Multisig Administration Costs: 5.000 ARB per month.\n\nNote: *We know that costs are out of date. In order to smooth the process we’ll keep the same operational costs until the release of Delegate Incentive System v1.1*",
