 Timeline and Milestones:**\n    \n    - **Milestone 1:** Successfully deploy the dPoints system on Arbitrum. Announcement by the end of Week 1.\n    - **Milestone 2:** Stablecoin pair TVL reaches $4 million, average daily volume reaches $6 million by the end of Week 4.\n    - **Milestone 3:** Stablecoin pair TVL reaches $6 million, average daily volume reaches $10 million by the end of Week 8.\n    - **Milestone 4:** Bridge stablecoin LP into the newly launched Orbit L3 DODOchain, ensuring sustainable TVL and trading volume for the pair after the incentive period ends by the end of Week 12.\n3. **TVL growth**\n    \n    DODO has recently announced the launch of the [layer 3 solution DODOchain](https://x.com/DODO_chain/status/1782431708752859395), the first restaked rollup powered by Arbitrum Orbit, focusing on integrating liquidity from other chains. Securing this LTIPP grant will significantly boost the TVL and trading volume on Arbitrum, attracting new users from other ecosystems, who will lock up their assets through our LP pairs on Arbitrum and eventually bridge to DODOchain through the official Arbitrum Bridge.",
