geting ~$3M daily volume\n* Incentivize fee rebate → less cost to trade → more trades → more volume and likely users\n* As Tradao is totally free to every user, we don’t charge any cost from users. This means all the costs are the gas fee and the fee charged by GMX. We will rebate 80% of open fees back to users. To achieve this, at a target of $3M daily volume and 100 daily transactions, across 12 weeks, it would require:\n  * USD equivalent = ($3M * 0.06% * 80%) * 365 * 12/52 = $121.29K\n  * ARB amount = $121.29K / $1.2 = 100K ARB at $1.2\n\n## Expected milestones\n\nInitial unlock 33% of ARB\n\nMilestone 1: 84m Trading Volume (66% of ARB unlocked & 33% of ARB distributed)\n\nMilestone 2: 168m Trading Volume (100% of ARB unlocked & 66% of ARB Distributed)\n\nMilestone 3: 252m Trading Volume (100% of ARB unlocked & 100% of ARB Distributed)\n\nThe Tradao team agrees to return to the Arbitrum DAO any unused ARB funds once the 12-week LTIPP program is concluded.",
