ollar equivalent of the trailing 14D ARB TWAP with a 30% buffer. After the ARB is swapped to USDC, any amount in excess of $309k will be immediately back to the DAO.\n\nThe scope of this proposal to the DAO is specifically for ETH CC in Brussels.",
