ite deckbuilder in one](https://questbook.app/dashboard/?grantId=0xbf93fc6825b5e9ba9a3d7fcf3d14cdfcf3b4c734\\&chainId=10\\&role=admin\\&proposalId=0x537\\&isRenderingProposalBody=true)\n   * Funding Approved for: 22.5k\n   * 0/2 Milestones Complete\n9. [Land, Labor and Capitol (LLC) - onchain tycoon game](https://www.questbook.app/dashboard/?grantId=0xbf93fc6825b5e9ba9a3d7fcf3d14cdfcf3b4c734\\&chainId=10\\&role=community\\&proposalId=0x4a1\\&isRenderingProposalBody=true)\n   * Funding Approved for: 18k\n   * 1/3 Milestones Complete\n   * [Milestone 1 - 6k Paid out](https://app.safe.global/transactions/tx?safe=undefined:0xebe67F2ceD2780321903CA7C6602C914262eb2DC\\&id=multisig_0xebe67F2ceD2780321903CA7C6602C914262eb2DC_0x96f6ff54f5125f618014e3640e165471621858fa0d8cd96c7a1df141c5e17b65)\n10. [Sponsorship of the Gaming Startup Collective’s Monthly Calendar of Events](https://www.questbook.app/dashboard/?grantId=0xbf93fc6825b5e9ba9a3d7fcf3d14cdfcf3b4c734\\&chainId=10\\&role=community\\&proposalId=0x53d\\&isRenderingProposalBody=true)\n    * Funding Approved for: 6.9k\n    * 1/3 Milestones Complete\n    * [Milestone 2 - 2.3k paid out](https://app.safe.global/transactions/tx?safe=undefined:0xebe67F2ceD2780321903CA7C6602C914262eb2DC\\&id=multisig_0xebe67F2ceD2780321903CA7C6602C914262eb2DC_0xeff7aec0787607b8a222001dec4c9b29c63dee1834917b112668211f6d61693a)\n11. [Chaquer- Fully On-Chain RTS Game](https://arbitrum.questbook.app/dashboard/?grantId=0xbf93fc6825b5e9ba9a3d7fcf3d14cdfcf3b4c734\\&chainId=10\\&role=community\\&proposalId=0x469\\&isRenderingProposalBody=true)\n    * Funding Approved for: 12k\n    * 1/3 Milestones Complete\n    * [Milestone 1 - 4k paid out](https://app.safe.global/transactions/tx?id=multisig_0xebe67F2ceD2780321903CA7C6602C914262eb2DC_0xed1e5314b1932003134f8b62d5773e64150f3077a872a00fab82c089427f8bd8\\&safe=arb1:0xebe67F2ceD2780321903CA7C6602C914262eb2DC)\n12. [Waypoint Gaming - Game Night Grant](https://arbitrum.questbook.app/dashboard/?grantId=0xbf93f