rant period. Overall, Factor's incentive strategy appears robust and well-thought-out, making it a compelling proposal for acceptance.\n*GFX Feedback) *\nOur main concern with this grant plan is requesting an amount that is nearly as much as the entire protocol’s TVL. The applicant scored highly in other areas, like composability, and solidly in most areas, which managed to offset the penalty to their score from the grant size. We recommend this grant be approved.",
