n. For instance, users could borrow against their BNB holdings on a different network and access USDC on Arbitrum. This design has the potential to broaden Arbitrum's liquidity base by tapping into external ecosystems while providing users with exposure to Arbitrum's low-cost environment. However, there is a need for more detailed information in the KPI and milestones section, particularly regarding the planned \"ramping up\" process, which requires clarification to ensure transparency and accountability in project execution.",
